'''積·保夫萊特'''（{{lang-en|'''Jay Bothroyd'''}}，{{bd|1982年|5月5日|catIdx=Bothroyd, Jay}}）是一名[[牙買加|牙買加]]裔[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，出身於[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]青訓系統，曾效力[[意甲|意甲]]球會[[佩魯賈足球會|佩魯賈]]及[[英超|英超]]球會[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]。現效力日職球會[[北海道札幌岡薩多|北海道札幌岡薩多]]。

==生平==
===球會===
====早期====
保夫萊特生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]伊斯灵顿（Islington），出身於[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]青訓系統，於1999年7月獲提供[[職業|職業]]球員合約，但沒有為一隊上過陣，期間曾為青年隊在決賽擊敗[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]贏得1999/2000年度[[英格蘭足總青年盃|英格蘭足總青年盃]]錦標，同期隊友包括[[史提夫·薛維爾|薛維爾]]、[[莫里茨·福尔茨|禾斯]]、[[杰雷米·阿利亚迭雷|艾利亞迪里]]等<ref name="happened at Arsenal">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/fa-league-cups/jay-bothroyd-i-try-not-to-look-back-on-what-happened-at-arsenal-1514374.html |title=Jay Bothroyd: 'I try not to look back on what happened at Arsenal' |publisher=''independent.co.uk'' |date=2009-01-24 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2019-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202172415/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/fa-league-cups/jay-bothroyd-i-try-not-to-look-back-on-what-happened-at-arsenal-1514374.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2000年5月[[英格蘭足球青年聯賽|英格蘭足球青年聯賽]]附加賽決賽對[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，當被領隊[[唐·豪伊|-{zh-hans:唐·豪伊; zh-hk:唐·侯爾;}-]]（Don Howe）換離場後，保夫萊特隨即脫衣並怒擲在後備席上表示不滿，事後球隊青年發展總監[[里亚姆·布拉迪|-{zh-hans:里亚姆·布拉迪; zh-hk:林·柏拉迪;}-]]發表聲明：『我們不會容忍這種行為，球會不再需要他。』其後將保夫萊特掛牌求售，7月6日[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]以100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]將保夫萊特收歸旗下<ref name="Coventry agree fee">{{cite news |language=en |title=Coventry agree fee for teenage striker |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/arsenal/822434.stm |publisher=''[[BBC|BBC]] Sport'' |date=2000-07-06 |accessdate=2000-07-06 }}</ref>。

====高雲地利====
保夫萊特效力高雲地利三年期間合共為球隊射入17球，但加盟的首年於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]處子出戰[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]後卻無甚貢獻，於2000年11月4日首次亮相[[英超|英超]]主場迎戰[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]以1-2落敗<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/1005606.stm |title=Man Utd deny spirited Coventry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2000-11-04 |accessdate=2010-10-30 |archive-date=2020-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901124152/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/1005606.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，球隊於季後降班[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英甲〈第二級〉]]。

保夫萊特是那類具有天份，但有時動機成疑及傾向敗壞氣質的球員，他於球隊陷於財困而出售大部分球員套現才獲機會擔正，在2001年8月24日作客1-2負於[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布拉德福德城; zh-hk:巴拉福特;}-]]射入個人首個入球；2002年1月29日作客對[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]，開賽10分鐘保夫萊特於25碼「笠」入先拔頭籌，但在完半場前與對方守將動武而雙雙被球證出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/1786484.stm |title=C Palace 1-3 Coventry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-01-29 |accessdate=2010-10-30 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307135021/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/1786484.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2001/02年球季他為球隊射入6球。翌季他以11個入球成為球隊首席射手，包括在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]8-0大勝[[鲁什登钻石足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:鲁什登钻石; zh-hk:魯斯頓鑽石;}-]]及聯賽作客2-1擊敗[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]兩仗[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/2281385.stm |title=Coventry 8-0 Rushden |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-10-02 |accessdate=2010-10-30 |archive-date=2020-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705090251/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/2281385.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2530737.stm |title=Stoke 1-2 Coventry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-12-07 |accessdate=2010-10-30 |archive-date=2020-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215124456/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2530737.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於球隊欠債高達2,500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，雖然貴為球隊首席射手，於季後約滿的保夫萊特仍不獲得領隊[[加利·麥亞里士打|加利·麥亞里士打]]留用<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11710_2263901,00.html |title=Sky Blues reveal debts |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-04-24 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308021842/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11710_2263901,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但卻獲得[[意甲|意甲]]的[[佩魯賈足球會|佩魯賈]]青睞<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11669_2269771,00.html |title=Bothroyd in Italian job |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-07-03 |accessdate=2010-11-02}}</ref>，於參加一場試訓賽事後，簽約三年正式加盟<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Bothroyd signs for Perugia |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/3058401.stm |work= |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2003-07-11 |accessdate=2003-07-11 |archive-date=2014-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140509032428/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/3058401.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====佩魯賈====
據稱由於高雲地利無法負擔保夫萊特每季約15萬[[歐元|歐元]]的薪金，[[佩魯賈足球會|佩魯賈]]的管理層觀看過他的比賽錄影帶後即安排試訓，僅48小時即落實用相同條件與保夫萊特簽約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11710_2277793,00.html |title=Perugia reveal Jay luck |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2003-10-18 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309144727/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11710_2277793,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。與保夫萊特同期加入佩魯賈的還有[[利比亞|利比亞]]領導人[[穆阿迈尔·卡扎菲|-{zh-hans:卡扎菲; zh-hk:卡達菲;}-]]的兒子[[阿尔-萨迪·卡扎菲|-{zh-hans:阿尔-萨迪·卡扎菲; zh-hk:薩德·卡達菲;}-]]（Al-Saadi al-Gaddafi）及擔任體能教練曾因服用[[兴奋剂|兴奋剂]]被终生禁赛的[[加拿大|加拿大]]前[[短跑|短跑]][[運動員|運動員]][[本·约翰逊_(田径运动员)|-{zh-hans:本·约翰逊; zh-hk:賓·莊遜;}-]]<ref name="happened at Arsenal"/>。2003年7月19日首次披甲，在[[欧洲足联国际托托杯|圖圖盃]]第三圈首回合主場迎戰[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]的AC艾倫斯（AC Allianssi），開賽後僅24分鐘即射入加盟後的首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11822_2271173,00.html |title=Bothroyd the hero for Perugia |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-07-19 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309154024/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11822_2271173,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主客兩回合同樣贏2-0；佩魯賈在準決賽淘汰[[南特足球會|南特]]後晉級[[2003年国际托托杯#決賽|決賽]]，對手為[[德甲|德甲]]的[[沃尔夫斯堡足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:沃尔夫斯堡; zh-hk:禾夫斯堡}-]]，8月12日主場保夫萊特射入唯一入球先勝1-0<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11844_2273197,00.html |title=Bothroyd gives Perugia the edge |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-08-12 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010706/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11844_2273197,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，次回合佩魯賈作客再勝2-0，累計3-0奪冠兼取得[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]參賽資格。8月31日[[意甲|意甲]]開鑼日，佩魯賈主場迎戰[[錫耶納足球俱樂部|錫耶納]]，保夫萊特為主隊射入第二球再領前2-1，是個人首個意甲入球，但最終仍被這支升班馬追平2-2完場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11860_2274838,00.html |title=Juve open in style |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-08-31 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310092806/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11860_2274838,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；保夫萊特在10月份再於[[博洛尼亞足球俱樂部|博洛尼亞]]及[[烏迪內斯足球俱樂部|烏甸尼斯]]身上各入一球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11861_2278796,00.html |title=Serie A Round-up |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2003-10-19 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309144707/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11861_2278796,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11862_2279386,00.html |title=Serie A round-up |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2003-10-26 |accessdate=2010-11-03}}</ref>。炙手可熱的保夫萊特受到各方注意，據報[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]的[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]、[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]、[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]及[[義大利|義大利]]本土的[[帕爾馬足球俱樂部|帕爾馬]]和[[拉齊奧足球俱樂部|拉素]]均對他虎視眈眈<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2275350,00.html |title=Bothroyd attracting interest |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-09-04 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310083551/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11674_2275350,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[錫耶納足球俱樂部|錫耶納]]更打算用[[尼古拉·文托拉|雲杜拿]]（Nicola Ventola）作交換條件<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11862_2284966,00.html |title=Jay happy despite Siena interest |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2003-12-30 |accessdate=2010-11-02}}</ref>，但最終保夫萊特下半季仍然留隊繼續效力。佩魯賈由於需要分心應付[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]賽事，[[2003年至2004年意大利足球甲级联赛|本土聯賽]]成績不濟，雖然煞科日憑保夫萊特的入球以1-0擊敗榜尾已篤定降班的[[安科納足球俱樂部|安科納]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11860_2299159,00.html |title=Serie A Round-Up |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2004-05-16 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309135556/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11860_2299159,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由於來季意甲擴大至20隊參賽，榜未3隊直接降班，佩魯賈以兩分差距將[[摩德纳足球俱乐部|摩德納]]及[[恩波利足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:恩波利; zh-hk:安玻里;}-]]直接推落[[意乙|意乙]]，而排第15位的佩魯賈要與意乙第6位的[[佛羅倫斯足球俱樂部|費倫天拿]]進行主客兩回合的附加賽爭取最後一個意甲席位，不幸累計1-2敗陣，來季降班意乙。

降班後的佩魯賈立即削減開支，[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]及[[法甲|法甲]]的[[索肖足球俱乐部|-{ zh-hans:索肖; zh-hk:索察;}-]]均對保夫萊特有興趣，但佩魯賈要求最少250萬[[歐元|歐元]]卻不獲合適的出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11706_2304359,00.html |title=Eagles chase Perugia ace |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2004-07-06 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217144249/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11706_2304359,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2004年夏季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前的8月31日，[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]成功獲得借用保夫萊特一個球季，並可於借用期滿後優先買斷<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Blackburn bring in Bothroyd |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/3616332.stm |work= |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-08-31 |accessdate=2004-08-31 |archive-date=2007-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071009220125/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/3616332.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月11日作客對[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]保夫萊特首次上陣，下半場後補入替[[布雷特·埃默顿|艾馬頓]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3599098.stm |title=Newcastle 3-0 Blackburn |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-09-11 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902083216/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3599098.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；10月30日主場2-2賽和[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]，保夫萊特射入扳平1-1的入球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/3947393.stm |title=Blackburn 2-2 Liverpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=30 October 2004 |accessdate=15 September 2009}}</ref>；11月6日作客對[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]，保夫萊特於完半場前粗暴腳踢對手而被球證直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3982685.stm |title=Norwich 1-1 Blackburn |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-11-06 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902082010/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3982685.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後他為自己的不當行為向領隊[[馬克·曉士|馬克·曉士]]、隊友及球迷致歉<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2315733,00.html |title=Bothroyd sorry for red |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2004-11-09 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217144227/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2315733,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月28日對[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]大腿受傷後需缺陣1個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2320569,00.html |title=Dickov happy to stay |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2004-12-28 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217144221/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2320569,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自此以後保夫萊特出場機會減少，僅在1月復出再戰保頓，直到2005年3月1日在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第五圈重賽主場對[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]才再獲派上陣，下半場59分鐘後補入替，僅維持了20分鐘便再次觸傷大腿舊患而被換離場，賽後被送往醫院檢查，並缺席餘下球季的賽事<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2328203,00.html |title=Triple blow for Rovers |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-03-02 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217144207/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2328203,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保夫萊特受到傷患困擾而影響演出，布力般流浪決定放棄優先買斷他的權利，借用期滿後返回佩魯賈。在2008年保夫萊特接受《南威爾斯回聲報》（South Wales Echo）訪問時透露，於[[義大利|義大利]]效力佩魯賈期間，當他或同隊其他[[黑人|黑人]]隊友觸球時，看台上的觀眾即作出[[种族主义|種族歧視]]扮[[猩猩|猩猩]]叫<ref>{{Cite web |language=en |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/11/15/bothroyd-talks-of-his-racism-agony-91466-22262821/ |title=Bothroyd talks of racism agony |publisher=''South Wales Echo'' |date=2008-11-15 |accessdate=2008-11-15 |archive-date=2009-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090813215422/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/11/15/bothroyd-talks-of-his-racism-agony-91466-22262821/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

佩魯賈於2004/05年球季在[[意乙|意乙]]位列第3位獲得參加升班附加賽，準決賽兩回合累計3-0淘汰[[特雷维索足球俱乐部|特雷維索]]，但決賽兩回合累計1-3負於[[都灵足球俱乐部|拖連奴]]無緣升班，而球會的財政問題亦逐漸浮現。保夫萊特表示希望留在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]，[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]及[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]均有意羅致<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2339345,00.html |title=Duo target Bothroyd |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-06-18 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308043651/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2339345,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他其後參加[[德甲|德甲]]球會[[柏林赫塔足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:柏林赫塔; zh-hk:哈化柏林}-]]的試訓<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2342404,00.html |title=Berlin trial for Bothroyd |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-07-19 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084158/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11676_2342404,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但不獲聘用<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11893_2344570,00.html |title=Bothroyd blows Berlin chance |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-08-12 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310092905/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11893_2344570,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；再前往[[美因茨05足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:美因茨05; zh-hk:緬恩斯;}-]]參加試訓<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11903_2345801,00.html |title=Mainz chance for Bothroyd |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2005-08-15 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309124737/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11903_2345801,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦沒有成果。

====查爾頓====
由於佩魯賈陷入財困，保夫萊特得以在2005年8月31日夏季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前，免費轉投由[[阿兰·柯比什利|古比士利]]帶領的[[英超|英超]]球會[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]，取代外借到[[蘇超|蘇超]][[流浪者足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:流浪者; zh-hk:格拉斯哥流浪;}-]]的[[弗朗西斯·杰弗斯|謝菲斯]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Bothroyd makes move to Charlton |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/charlton_athletic/4203282.stm |work= |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2005-08-31 |accessdate=2005-08-31 }}</ref>，但仍需要與較早來投的[[戴倫·賓特|戴倫·賓特]]競逐正選前鋒席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2347723,00.html |title=Jay ready to settle down |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-09-01 |accessdate=2010-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309124741/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2347723,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月20日於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第二圈主場對[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:哈特尔普尔; zh-hk:哈特普爾;}-]]，保夫萊特下半場首次後補入替，即錦上添花射入一球為球隊鎖定3-1勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/football/match_report/0,19764,11065_2561773,00.html |title=Addicks battle past Pools |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-09-20 |accessdate=2010-11-03}}</ref>。由於在球季展開後才加盟查爾頓，古比士利以其狀態不足，季初僅派他上陣兩場，直到10月在[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]對[[埃克塞特城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:埃克塞特城; zh-hk:艾斯特城;}-]]演出[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2351453,00.html |title=Curbs welcomes back duo |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-10-12 |accessdate=2010-11-04}}</ref>，才於10月17日主場對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]的「倫敦打吡」再獲派上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4322130.stm |title=Charlton 1-1 Fulham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2005-10-17 |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822201341/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4322130.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保夫萊特在查爾頓最大的貢獻來自其強勁的[[自由球|自由球]]，對[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]時在禁區邊緣直射破網，取得加盟後首個[[英超|英超]]入球<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/4473114.stm |title=Charlton 2-5 Man City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=4 December 2005 |accessdate=15 September 2009}}</ref>，他另一個英超入球來自對[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]的近門頂入<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/4820064.stm |title=Charlton 3-1 Newcastle |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=26 March 2006 |accessdate=15 September 2009 |archive-date=2007-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070118061104/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/4820064.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，另外在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第五圈對[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布伦特福德; zh-hk:賓福特;}-]]亦轟入一個自由球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/4703830.stm |title=Charlton 3-1 Brentford |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-02-18 |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309195319/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/4703830.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2005年12月12日保夫萊特在駕駛途中突然[[昏厥|昏厥]]導致撞車，事後他完全不能憶述事發經過，據報六年前亦曾發生相同事件，其健康情況受到關注<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2357713,00.html |title=Charlton concern for Jay |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-12-13 |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085051/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2357713,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，保夫萊特接受神經系統試驗希望找出病因，有猜測因[[毒品|藥物]]或[[乙醇|酒精]]引致意外，但保夫萊特作出否認<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2357304,00.html |title=Bothroyd blasts slurs |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2005-12-15 |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309135229/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2357304,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

雖然有傳[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]及[[意甲|意甲]]的[[烏迪內斯足球俱樂部|烏甸尼斯]]及[[佛羅倫斯足球俱樂部|費倫天拿]]有意在冬季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]羅致未能融入查爾頓的保夫萊特<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11681_2363749,00.html |title=Trio target Bothroyd |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-01-16 |accessdate=2010-11-04}}</ref>，僅簽約一年的保夫萊特卻表示希望留隊爭取表現<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2365329,00.html |title=Jay hopes for Addicks stay |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-01-29 |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085056/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2365329,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整季上陣25場僅有4場正選及只有5個入球，保夫萊特仍希望獲得查爾頓提供新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2373703,00.html |title=Bothroyd wants Addicks stay |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-04-16 |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309161458/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2373703,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但隨著新領隊[[伊恩·杜尼|伊恩·杜尼]]（Iain Dowie）上場，他成為首兩名被放棄的球員之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2378712,00.html |title=Dowie in quick cull |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-05-31 |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041818/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11684_2378712,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

保夫萊特獲[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]邀請參加季前訓練，領隊[[彼得·泰勒|彼得·泰萊]]正在找尋取代離隊的[[安祖·莊臣|安祖·莊臣]]的前鋒人選，保夫萊特橫渡[[大西洋|大西洋]]與正在[[美國|美國]]的球隊會合，並在3-1擊敗[[巴爾的摩水晶宮|美國水晶宮]]（Crystal Palace F.C. USA）的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]穿上沒有背號的球衣上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11706_2383994,00.html |title=Palace chance for Bothroyd |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2006-07-18 |accessdate=2010-11-05 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308035611/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11706_2383994,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並為球隊先拔頭籌<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.croydonguardian.co.uk/news/839012.eagles_start_us_tour_with_victory/ |title=Eagles start US tour with victory |publisher=''croydonguardian.co.uk'' |date=2006-07-18 |accessdate=2010-11-05 |archive-date=2017-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623043823/http://www.croydonguardian.co.uk/news/839012.eagles_start_us_tour_with_victory/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最終沒有獲得聘用，保夫萊特其後否認曾參加水晶宮的試訓，只是友情客串參賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Bothroyd denies Palace trial |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11699_2411244,00.html |work= |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2007-04-14 |accessdate=2007-04-14 |archive-date=2016-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230074930/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11699_2411244,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
